<subSubSection id="10EB7FA22E093508BD89F453B2E34F3F" pageId="null" pageNumber="45" type="description">
<paragraph id="61EBC590E7E19542FA9AF2F020C6F6DC" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="6EB1EA32E46057A2D28EDF729085E1F5" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Thalictrum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="45" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bauhinii">
<emphasis id="FBF3C0D711F09AA41CF13E20E160FD02" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">T. Bauhinii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 4a) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="E6CA2444A4D3E65E9C4C90A762941AC6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">
Alle 
<normalizedToken id="2F1C104D29D3F04CAC8154178A4F71E0" originalValue="Teilblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">Teilblaetter</normalizedToken>
schmal lanzettlich bis 
<normalizedToken id="B73D963597D5934DE4CA5C15883FE5A2" originalValue="fadenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">fadenfoermig</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="8F88CE2A101FEA0704BC31AD6528797D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">10-20mal so lang wie breit</emphasis>
), 
<emphasis id="0FC8127E7A414E1E62CAAA96720B2694" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">die meisten ganzrandig</emphasis>
(ausgenommen an 
<normalizedToken id="93AC03980DD61AFA9A1603E4C2C9EB45" originalValue="grundständigen" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">grundstaendigen</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="6A9B0D9829A976FA64A26968514D54C5" originalValue="Blättern" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">Blaettern</normalizedToken>
). - 
<normalizedToken id="6EA76B338CE11265661AF9472FA0F30E" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C17FEB53243EBF662AD10180E07E1FC8" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis id="61841167229F02E6C5B56B6F874640E8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="A47B828609424222473E0780215E3828" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">28:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="287313BB9986FD38BEB3B1A8646B00A4" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Kuhn 1928).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="76E0382D671A9B169635154F2DEC9430" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis id="68F8FFFAE6DCA785E1752DC2AA1C122E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">Standort.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="57D852E563E7083AA6107E5C7933CA0B" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Thalictrum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="45" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bauhinii">
<emphasis id="460B9444397A9A2A3BD563FD23583B9F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">T. Bauhinii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 4a).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7B5C67C90DC0DC85A298CF7A1CED5813" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis id="7F2DE1018EB0CB12123D2F1D75FD4E17" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">Verbreitung.</emphasis>
Wenig bekannt, Zentral- und 
<normalizedToken id="F8A501BC5F77CDE4191C4B6A10F7F474" originalValue="Südosteuropa" pageId="null" pageNumber="45">Suedosteuropa</normalizedToken>
. - Im Gebiet ziemlich verbreitet, ziemlich selten.
</paragraph>
